Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,香織啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我還好 就是有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧 始他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一個人嗎 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,火山噴發是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那始他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 應該會跟在我後面回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,主人沒有絲毫放棄的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是有什麼計策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 主人叫我傳話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 準確來說是說給你和繆的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他說「待會再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那肯定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就算身處絕望險境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,主人也一定能奇蹟生還
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,相信他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不去接爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得相信始爸爸 完成好我們手上的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這之後再去接他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 不能把繆帶去古盧恩大火山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先去愛尼森 讓繆和媽媽見面怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後過了多少天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,始 感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題 不過痊癒還需要點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事 畢竟希婭讓我吸了血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,月小姐 你為什麼要坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,極光的毒素基本都排出來了 應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我都說了沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 還是很讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這地方讓人擔心 不過能好好休息就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 畢竟事情那麼跌宕起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道是幸運還是倒楣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,暫時放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,始 看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是魔法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這是 空間操作魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是瞬間移動的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那種突然出現在背後的是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,祈願人的未來 為自由之意志所掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奈茲·古盧恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太簡單了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺就像無事一身輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,奈茲大人除了魔法好像沒留下其他任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 攻略證明和魔法都到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就看怎麼逃出這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是空間魔法很難掌控 沒辦法立刻使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你有計策對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,外面應該已經完全被岩漿淹沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在岩漿裡游著前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託 別像看傻子一樣看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我準備了潛水用的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想著之後梅爾基涅海底遺跡肯定用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以提前做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就看能不能擋得住岩漿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看來沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 船舵不聽使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要是火山噴發把我們噴出去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,徑直往下…不對 好像在往斜下方走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那…就是說我們在往地底下鑽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,月 希婭 看來短時間內是回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只能先逃到能去的地方再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直陪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能陪著你我別無他求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣 就算上刀山下火海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能和你們在一起 我也願意奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 彈藥用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,月 吸我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我還…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,二位 你們是不是忘了個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,吸我的血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,吸了她很多血 暫時應該不會醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了啊 感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝你若無其事泰然自若的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心情非常愉快 簡直好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡到底是哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 雖然我很想調查一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是寶物庫給了緹奧 我也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走一步算一步的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就是遇難了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是什麼人 為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這騎乘工具是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,休想引開我們的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就是這樣誘拐了那孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你們又來誘拐我們的小孩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是說繆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴 區區一個兔人族少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛好像有東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,繆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,繆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再做這麼危險的事了 能答應我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所見 生龍活虎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 所以你別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,香織一哭我就頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再讓我靠一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你 我一直相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是能像這樣重逢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,給我點時間 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,來 主人 快獎勵我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那個小女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 應該就是蕾蜜雅被拐走的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,確認公會支部長的委託完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,金級冒險者 南雲閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,想必你們也有很多問題想問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我想先讓這孩子見見她母親 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,海上被人目擊的龍和船一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,作為王國士兵實在不能視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們打算在愛尼森滯留一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有空再詳細解釋可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,既然有機會詳聊那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等你們安頓好了再來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我說完了 不要繼續圍觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我會以妨礙王國士兵公務為由逮捕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快回家 媽媽還等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想見媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 趕緊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅你冷靜點 你的腿走不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 蕾蜜雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會把繆帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 繆不是回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,繆 繆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是我沒保護好你 對不起 繆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的 媽媽 繆就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,繆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 你的腿怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,受傷了嗎 很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快來救救媽媽 媽媽的腿很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,繆 你剛剛說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 果然你說的是爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？是叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你想屁吃 當然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 繆 很快就能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 別這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅再婚了？不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅也終於迎來了第二春 可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 這傷是被拐走繆的那些人害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題 能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不留後遺症
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,花點時間慢慢痊癒會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,痊癒之前會有些不便 不過一定能恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我還聽說這傷無人能醫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真不知道該如何感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…說起來 你們和繆是如何相遇的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼繆會叫你爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,說來話長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,能再次見到女兒都是多虧了各位的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我會窮盡一生報答這份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客氣 您可是繆的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你們要在這裡滯留一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不如就住在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣繆也會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 不用擔心我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,棧橋附近正好有家好住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我還想把船修一修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 爸爸放下女兒不管可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你們總有一天還要再出發 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為如此 分別之前就好好當她的爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是說只能到分別的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一直當她的爸爸也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我也說了我會用一輩子報答這份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這種玩笑就別開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒見氣氛都變陰冷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我的丈夫去世也快5年了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,繆也想要爸爸對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？爸爸就是爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 緊急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 剛剛她說了先去向陛下報告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,八重檻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,關於清水的事情很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 很開心老師能倖存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真得好好謝謝南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是他去救你們了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還照顧著一個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定他正慢慢找回曾經的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,或者說是在變化中慢慢成長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,太可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 聽說他在危難之中救了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,具體情況是怎樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 既然都說差點喪命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定還是很在意到底是怎麼得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,您和南雲之間發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 還能有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他就是普通的師生關係而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 冷靜點 你說話都變奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲 你對小愛做了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 你向陛下報告的時候發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他們正式認定南云為異端分子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 這樣下定論未免太草率了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是不服從教會的強大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但從結論來說南雲的確拯救了烏爾鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不管怎麼抗議他們就是不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,明明他們應該不能無視我的抗議才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,將南雲認定為異端分子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就等於否定了豐收女神的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很明顯不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,現在回想起來 陛下他們的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,的確讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他們到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲已經很強了 他們還能派誰去找他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,八重檻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有些話南雲只告訴了我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 關於教會祭拜的神 還有南雲的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然毫無證據
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這件事非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得必須儘早告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 海底的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:24.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:30.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:35.99,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:42.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:47.84,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:51.59,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.43,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:59.35,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:05.31,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:11.03,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:16.45,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.70,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:25.04,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
